>>DROPOUT 
        > turn off random neurons 
        > we use them after activation(relu) and give a p value(the percent of neurons to turn off)

>> BATCH NORMALIZATION 
        > done before activation 
        > normalize the hidden layer activations

>>L2 REGULARISATION 
        > we add a penalty term in loss and now we have to reduce it to we put penalty term to weights and not bias 
        > in l2 its the summation of weights squared
        > penalize large weights and distribute it to other weights to reduce dependency from one particular weights